Package: steamr
Type: Package
Title: R Interface to Steam's APIs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jonas", "Lieth", , "jonas.lieth@gesis.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: R interface to the Steam Web API and storefront API. Performs
    standardized API calls, session authentication, key management, Steam ID
    conversion and response formatting. Provides tools for data scraping of
    game details, user reviews, store economy data, news, and many more.
    Can read and parse Steam's KeyValues format. Also provides access to
    external services such as SteamSpy, steamcmd.net, and Steam location
    geocoding.
